{
  "id": "adv_group_moon_05_03",
  "title": "月のテンペスト 05 03",
  "script": [
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyoktnroom-00-night.webp",
      "bgName": "tokyoktnroom-00-night",
      "startTime": 0
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ngs",
      "speakerName": "伊吹渚",
      "speakerNameEn": "Nagisa",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-nagisa.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/extraStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_group_moon_05_03/sud_vo_adv_group_moon_05_03-ngs001.m4a",
      "text": "私達が中二の時、麻奈さんは人気絶頂で\nテレビや雑誌で麻奈さんを見ない日はなかったよね",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Mana-san was at the height of her popularity when we were in the second year of middle school‚\nThere wasn't a day when we didn't see her on TV or in magazines‚ huh?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 0.8,
      "endTime": 8.6595235825,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyoktnroom-00-night.webp",
      "bgName": "tokyoktnroom-00-night",
      "startTime": 8.8528566678
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ktn",
      "speakerName": "長瀬琴乃",
      "speakerNameEn": "Kotono",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kotono.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/extraStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_group_moon_05_03/sud_vo_adv_group_moon_05_03-ktn001.m4a",
      "text": "私はアイドルを続けるお姉ちゃんに反発して\n家でも距離を置いていたのに……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "I was rebelling against my sister who kept being an idol‚\nand I was keeping my distance from her even at home…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 8.8528566678,
      "endTime": 15.314625295,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyoktnroom-00-night.webp",
      "bgName": "tokyoktnroom-00-night",
      "startTime": 15.4879587174
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ktn",
      "speakerName": "長瀬琴乃",
      "speakerNameEn": "Kotono",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kotono.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/extraStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_group_moon_05_03/sud_vo_adv_group_moon_05_03-ktn002.m4a",
      "text": "街を歩けばお姉ちゃんのポスターが貼ってあるし\nお店に入ればお姉ちゃんの曲が流れてるし……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "If I walked down the street‚ there would be posters of my sister‚\nand if I went into a store‚ her song would be playing…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 15.4879587174,
      "endTime": 24.5304761887,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ktn",
      "speakerName": "長瀬琴乃",
      "speakerNameEn": "Kotono",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kotono.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/extraStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_group_moon_05_03/sud_vo_adv_group_moon_05_03-ktn003.m4a",
      "text": "学校に行けば、お姉ちゃんに会わせてとか\nサインがほしいとか散々言われて……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "If I went to school‚ I'd be asked to introduce them to my sister‚\nor get her autograph‚ I was told all the time…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 24.7438095411,
      "endTime": 31.7360316595,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyoktnroom-00-night.webp",
      "bgName": "tokyoktnroom-00-night",
      "startTime": 31.929365031
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ngs",
      "speakerName": "伊吹渚",
      "speakerNameEn": "Nagisa",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-nagisa.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/extraStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_group_moon_05_03/sud_vo_adv_group_moon_05_03-ngs002.m4a",
      "text": "どこに行っても麻奈さんが追いかけてくるみたいで\n気が休まらないって、いつも言ってたよね",
      "translations": {
        "en": "It was like Mana-san was following you wherever you went‚\nYou always said you never had a day to rest‚ right?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 31.929365031,
      "endTime": 38.4791156453,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyoktnroom-00-night.webp",
      "bgName": "tokyoktnroom-00-night",
      "startTime": 38.6657821974
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ktn",
      "speakerName": "長瀬琴乃",
      "speakerNameEn": "Kotono",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kotono.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/extraStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_group_moon_05_03/sud_vo_adv_group_moon_05_03-ktn004.m4a",
      "text": "あの頃は渚によく愚痴を聞いてもらったわね\n私が気を許せる相手は渚だけだったから",
      "translations": {
        "en": "You often listened to my complaints back then‚ Nagisa.\nYou were the only one I could open up to‚ Nagisa.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 38.6657821974,
      "endTime": 47.424172433200006,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_famires-00-night.webp",
      "bgName": "famires-00-night",
      "startTime": 48.6208384197
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_famires-00-night.webp",
      "bgName": "famires-00-night",
      "startTime": 48.6208384197
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ngs",
      "speakerName": "伊吹渚",
      "speakerNameEn": "Nagisa",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-nagisa.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/extraStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_group_moon_05_03/sud_vo_adv_group_moon_05_03-ngs003.m4a",
      "text": "そういえば麻奈さん、またニュースになってたね\n東京レイーズの動員記録を更新したんだっけ？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Now that I think about it‚ Mana-san was in the news again.\nDid she break the attendance record for Tokyo Rays or something?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 49.6708384197,
      "endTime": 57.5682762783,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_famires-00-night.webp",
      "bgName": "famires-00-night",
      "startTime": 57.7816096307
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ktn",
      "speakerName": "長瀬琴乃",
      "speakerNameEn": "Kotono",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kotono.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/extraStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_group_moon_05_03/sud_vo_adv_group_moon_05_03-ktn005.m4a",
      "text": "もう、渚までやめてよ。どこに行っても\nお姉ちゃんの話ばかりでうんざりしてるんだから",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Seriously‚ Nagisa‚ you too‚ stop it. No matter where I go\nI'm sick of hearing about my sister all the time.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 57.7816096307,
      "endTime": 65.2032197953,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_famires-00-night.webp",
      "bgName": "famires-00-night",
      "startTime": 65.4032198907
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ktn",
      "speakerName": "長瀬琴乃",
      "speakerNameEn": "Kotono",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kotono.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/extraStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_group_moon_05_03/sud_vo_adv_group_moon_05_03-ktn006.m4a",
      "text": "はぁ……どうしたらお姉ちゃんは\nアイドルを辞めてくれるんだろう……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Sigh… What can I do to make my sister\nquit being an idol…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 65.4032198907,
      "endTime": 71.8509521484,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_famires-00-night.webp",
      "bgName": "famires-00-night",
      "startTime": 72.0376187961
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ngs",
      "speakerName": "伊吹渚",
      "speakerNameEn": "Nagisa",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-nagisa.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/extraStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_group_moon_05_03/sud_vo_adv_group_moon_05_03-ngs004.m4a",
      "text": "麻奈さんは琴乃ちゃんのことが大好きだから\n琴乃ちゃんのお願いなら聞いてくれそうだけど……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Mana-san loves you so much‚ Kotono‚\nso I think she'd listen to you if you asked…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 72.0376187961,
      "endTime": 79.14682528179999,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_famires-00-night.webp",
      "bgName": "famires-00-night",
      "startTime": 79.3601586342
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ktn",
      "speakerName": "長瀬琴乃",
      "speakerNameEn": "Kotono",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kotono.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/extraStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_group_moon_05_03/sud_vo_adv_group_moon_05_03-ktn007.m4a",
      "text": "私が何度頼んでもダメだったことは\n渚も知ってるでしょ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "You know that no matter how many times I asked her‚ she wouldn't listen.\nYou know that too‚ Nagisa.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 79.3601586342,
      "endTime": 84.03814029700001,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ktn",
      "speakerName": "長瀬琴乃",
      "speakerNameEn": "Kotono",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kotono.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/extraStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_group_moon_05_03/sud_vo_adv_group_moon_05_03-ktn008.m4a",
      "text": "前にお姉ちゃんに聞いたことがあるの\n「私とアイドルの仕事、どっちが好きなの？」って",
      "translations": {
        "en": "I asked my sister before.\n\"Which do you like more‚ me or your idol work?\"",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 84.238140297,
      "endTime": 90.8969383241,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_famires-00-night.webp",
      "bgName": "famires-00-night",
      "startTime": 91.0969384194
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ktn",
      "speakerName": "長瀬琴乃",
      "speakerNameEn": "Kotono",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kotono.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/extraStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_group_moon_05_03/sud_vo_adv_group_moon_05_03-ktn009.m4a",
      "text": "そしたらお姉ちゃん、「両方とも大好きだよ」って\n悪びれもせずに言ったのよ！　許せないと思わない！？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Then she said‚ \"I love both of them so much‚\"\nwithout even feeling bad! Can you believe it!?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 91.0969384194,
      "endTime": 98.4651242258,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_famires-00-night.webp",
      "bgName": "famires-00-night",
      "startTime": 98.678457292
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ngs",
      "speakerName": "伊吹渚",
      "speakerNameEn": "Nagisa",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-nagisa.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/extraStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_group_moon_05_03/sud_vo_adv_group_moon_05_03-ngs005.m4a",
      "text": "はいはい、落ち着いて。イライラした時は\n甘い物を食べるといいよ。はい、あーん",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Alright alright‚ calm down. When you're irritated‚\neating something sweet is good. Here‚ aah.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 98.678457292,
      "endTime": 106.5646022162,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_famires-00-night.webp",
      "bgName": "famires-00-night",
      "startTime": 104.68
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_famires-00-night.webp",
      "bgName": "famires-00-night",
      "startTime": 106.7512690546
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ktn",
      "speakerName": "長瀬琴乃",
      "speakerNameEn": "Kotono",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kotono.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/extraStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_group_moon_05_03/sud_vo_adv_group_moon_05_03-ktn010.m4a",
      "text": "もう……\n…………あーん",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Seriously…\n…Aah.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 106.7512690546,
      "endTime": 112.8230605126,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_famires-00-night.webp",
      "bgName": "famires-00-night",
      "startTime": 113.0163938841
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ngs",
      "speakerName": "伊吹渚",
      "speakerNameEn": "Nagisa",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-nagisa.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/extraStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_group_moon_05_03/sud_vo_adv_group_moon_05_03-ngs006.m4a",
      "text": "家でも会わないようにしてるみたいだけど\n琴乃ちゃんは麻奈さんと会えなくて寂しくないの？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "You seem to be trying to avoid seeing her even at home‚ but\nAren't you lonely because you can't see Mana-san‚ Kotono?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 113.0163938841,
      "endTime": 119.91158679339999,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_famires-00-night.webp",
      "bgName": "famires-00-night",
      "startTime": 120.0982533456
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ktn",
      "speakerName": "長瀬琴乃",
      "speakerNameEn": "Kotono",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kotono.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/extraStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_group_moon_05_03/sud_vo_adv_group_moon_05_03-ktn011.m4a",
      "text": "そりゃあ寂しいけど……\n私には渚がいるから平気よ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Of course I'm lonely‚ but…\nI'm fine because I have you‚ Nagisa.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 120.0982533456,
      "endTime": 127.1132191659,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_famires-00-night.webp",
      "bgName": "famires-00-night",
      "startTime": 127.3265524706
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ngs",
      "speakerName": "伊吹渚",
      "speakerNameEn": "Nagisa",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-nagisa.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/extraStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_group_moon_05_03/sud_vo_adv_group_moon_05_03-ngs007.m4a",
      "text": "……姉妹で仲良くしてほしいけど、そう言われるともう\nちょっとだけ今のままでもいいかなって思っちゃうな～",
      "translations": {
        "en": "I wish you two would get along‚ but hearing you say that makes me\nthink maybe it's okay the way things are now~",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 127.3265524706,
      "endTime": 136.2273691973,
      "sfxList": [
        {
          "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_se_adv_message-01.m4a",
          "delay": 9106.780862699992,
          "startTime": 136.4333333333
        },
        {
          "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_se_adv_phone-tap-02.m4a",
          "delay": 12473.447529400004,
          "startTime": 139.8
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_famires-00-night.webp",
      "bgName": "famires-00-night",
      "startTime": 136.4333333333
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ktn",
      "speakerName": "長瀬琴乃",
      "speakerNameEn": "Kotono",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kotono.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/extraStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_group_moon_05_03/sud_vo_adv_group_moon_05_03-ktn012.m4a",
      "text": "……あ、お姉ちゃんからメッセだ\n遊園地のチケットをもらったから一緒に行こうって……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "…Ah‚ it’s a message from my sister\nShe got tickets to the amusement park‚ and she’s asking me to go with her",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 139.1,
      "endTime": 147.63820877080002,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_famires-00-night.webp",
      "bgName": "famires-00-night",
      "startTime": 147.8655750118
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ngs",
      "speakerName": "伊吹渚",
      "speakerNameEn": "Nagisa",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-nagisa.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/extraStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_group_moon_05_03/sud_vo_adv_group_moon_05_03-ngs008.m4a",
      "text": "麻奈さんと一緒に遊園地かー。楽しそうだね\n……って、琴乃ちゃん？　どうして険しい顔してるの？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "You're going to the amusement park with Mana-san. That sounds fun.\n…Hey‚ Kotono? Why are you making such a face?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 147.8655750118,
      "endTime": 159.4242820584,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_famires-00-night.webp",
      "bgName": "famires-00-night",
      "startTime": 153.3333305996
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_famires-00-night.webp",
      "bgName": "famires-00-night",
      "startTime": 159.6242818676
