      "text": "うん……映画も面白かったけど、それ以上に\n久しぶりにお姉ちゃんと一緒に過ごせたのが嬉しかった",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Yeah… The movie was interesting‚ but even more than that‚\nI was happy to be able to spend time with my sister after so long.",
